{"tid":700061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無絲打同我一樣","createTime":"2018-06-13T04:51:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T11:20:03.000Z","uid":185196,"like":7,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c4996e2a51b37e10cde3a3c9ab1ccf6641ee5248","tid":700061,"uid":185196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:51:29.000Z","msg":"同我一樣好鐘意俾男朋友抱住<br />\n一啲空間都無，貼住哂。<br />\n好有安全感就算佢啲臭汗我都好鐘意<br />\n電梯一直企係你後面唔俾人睇洩曬。<br />\n真係好窩心嫁。<br />\n<br />\n仲有俾佢填滿自己嘅時候真係好舒服<br />\n唔係話生理上而係愛呀<br />\n同埋滿足到佢嘅感覺真係好奇妙<br />\n就算要我扮高潮都好要我食藥都好我都唔會介意<br />\n因為我真係好愛佢。<br />\n<br />\n其實我地只係需要另一半日常嘅細微野<br />\n好鐘意男朋友件外套因爲o個陣味真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我愛你呀 小誠誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d6c7faa7d8c004dd843da79a27ed0b170502f4","tid":700061,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50c067b09557a129897fdb540f8472826cd8c6b9","tid":700061,"uid":185196,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"26d6c7faa7d8c004dd843da79a27ed0b170502f4","tid":700061,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"對唔住 我中學都未讀完 只係想分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝糾正我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係就會錯一世了<br />\n我會永記心中的"},{"pid":"70e5109bb20d195675f9019189378297b0268e36","tid":700061,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:56:11.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"360117c563c96bef9e07f0af3208edd39c182495","tid":700061,"uid":185196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70e5109bb20d19567